<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="119r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_241_r2l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft cʒü <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / Vicʒtüm in Nydern Beyrn / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l2">Lıeber her Vicʒtüm / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von der ladung
                        wegen / als des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l3"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>vveiſſemburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> hawſfraw die von Regenſpurg lad / .
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l4">vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd
                                <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr erberkeit vviſſen / daʒ
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>vveiſſemburg<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l5">mer vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıſt / . vnd
                        ſind er vnd ſein hawſfraw <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l6">von geltſchuld wegen / . Alſo / daʒ vvir Jr nicht
                        mechtig ſein vnd darcʒü nichts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l7">getün künnen / . weren <add><ab facs="#facs_241_line_1576749910396_9204">ſie </ab></add> aber noch
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvas wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l8">getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        cʒemal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> getan / als vvir auch vor / die vveil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l9">wir Jr mechtig vvaren getan
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vvan wo vvir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l10">vnd dienſt beweiſen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> /
                        Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir allcʒeit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ̃ . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l11"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Oſwaldȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_241" id="119r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft czü
                            <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztüm in Nydern Beyrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vicztüm, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt von der ladung wegen, als des <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Weissemburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> hawsfraw die von Regenspurg lad,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr
                        erberkeit wissen, daz <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Weissemburg<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht mer unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ist; und sind er und sein hawsfraw
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                        geltschuld wegen, also daz wir ir nicht mechtig sein und darczü nichts getün
                        künnen. Weren <add>sie</add> aber noch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, was wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czemal
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> getan, als wir auch vor, die weil wir
                        ir mechtig waren, getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wan wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dienst beweisen
                                <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Oswaldi.</ab>
</div>
